Littlelife klamboe kinderwagen

description.en:
Littlelife mosquito net pram 

This stroller mosquito net offers 100% protection against all kinds of insects. The mosquito net has a universal fit and fits most strollers. The mosquito net is easy to attach by stretching it over the buggy and is tear resistant, breathable and durable 

Specifications:
Colour: white
Gender: unisex
Material: polyester, mesh
Size: one-size
